
---

## `.gitignore` (paste at project root)

```gitignore
# ---- Python / venv
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.so
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
.env
.env.*

# ---- Jupyter / notebooks
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ---- OS/editor cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*.VSCodeCounter/
.vscode/
.idea/

# ---- Logs & caches
*.log
logs/
.cache/
huggingface/
datasets-cache/
wandb/

# ---- Artifacts & checkpoints
artifacts/**/checkpoint-*/
artifacts/**/*.pt
artifacts/**/*.bin
artifacts/**/*.safetensors
artifacts/**/*.ckpt
artifacts/**/*.pth
artifacts/**/*.onnx

# Keep result summaries & plots but ignore heavy weights by default
!artifacts/**/results.json
!artifacts/**/kimcnn_results.json
!artifacts/**/bilstm_results.json
!artifacts/**/summary.md
!artifacts/**/*.png

# ---- Data (keep folder, ignore raw files by default)
data/*
!data/.gitkeep
# If you want to track the CSV, comment the line above and add:
# !data/all-data.csv

# ---- Reports (keep Markdown)
reports/*.html
reports/*.pdf
# Keep README.md
!reports/README.md

# ---- Experiments (if you add configs later)
experiments/*.log
experiments/*.tmp
